reviews.customers_say: Customers find this cashmere sweater well-made and appreciate its generous length, with one noting it's not too tight. Customers find it comfortable, noting it doesn't itch at all, though opinions about thickness are mixed, with some finding it beautifully thick while others say it's a bit thin.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Ok quality cashmere
items.body: great sweater! fits perfectly for a fitted sweater and soft cashmere Read more
items.author: jenn

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars The quality seems to be pretty good.
items.body: Lovely color, nice feel to the cashmere. Read more
items.author: KC

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great Quality
items.body: I'll start with the pluses. The blue color is heavenly. The material is soft and plush - you definitely feel the quality. And while hand washing, I was pleasantly surprised: Very little lint that you normally get when washing cashmere. My one gripe is in the style. Just not crazy about the large neckband. Don't find it that flattering, and wish it were thinner. The tighter stylish cut of this sweater doesn't quite work with my plump figure, (why I bought extra large). It does look good, but the cheaper sweaters seem more flattering for this tubby. I'll finish by saying this is definitely a keeper. And I highly recommend this sweater as a gift. Read more
items.author: jharles

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars It is a gorgeous sweater.
items.body: I love this sweater. The cashmere is so soft and warm at the same time not bulky . I love the color it is perfect for me. Read more
items.author: Janice Adams

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful, Quality Cashmere
items.body: Beautiful quality cashmere! I'm 5'9" 36ddd 28 37 with long arms and legs, usually a size 8 in tops. I ordered a large. The fit is stellar! Relaxed, which is what I wanted. I wanted a relaxed fit and wanted certainty that the sleeves would be long enough. I could've worn a Medium for a more tailored look. This sweater is great, relaxed but not too big and the sleeves are the perfect length too. Super soft, comfy and cozy sweater. Love it! ****Update**** December 13, 2015 I decided to order two more of these sweaters, one red and another navy both size Medium. What happened? These two are not of the same quality as the first one that I bought. The cashmere is short and the sweater's stitches can be seen because the lovely cashmere furrieness that made my first one so lovely is non-exsistant on these two and they are scratchy! I won't be buying anymore; a total bait and switch! Not cool at all!! Read more
items.author: P. Gray

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to wear. Lovely color
items.body: Easy to wear. The color is awesome. Simple and elegant Read more

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Happy with this sweater.
items.body: Bought the dark teal color and it is beautiful. I am 5"0' and weight 120 lbs. The medium was the right size. Read more
items.author: Kimmie

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Smaller than expected
items.body: This fit smaller than expected. I ordered a medium and it was snug and also a bit itchy. It would be beautiful in a size larger. I had hoped for softer material given the price. Read more

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

This piece transitions well from daytime plans to evening events with a quick change of shoes and a small bag or clutch.

The design is easy to style with simple accessories and works well in photos thanks to clean lines and a balanced silhouette.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: One Size.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Orchid, Petal Pink, Sky, Aqua, Blue, Cream, Lt Grey, Chocolate, Black, Tomato, Oatmeal, Azalea, Red, Lime. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
